77
00:06:57,879 --> 00:07:00,720
Officer, I'm really innocent.

78
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:03,079
I thought he was a scammer,

79
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:05,399
who disguised himself
as a university student

80
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:08,199
to rob old ladies
who live alone like me.

81
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,240
I'm innocent.

82
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:32,100
She always complained about being poor

83
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:34,600
but took out such a large sum of money
before she died.

84
00:07:35,253 --> 00:07:37,310
